# cozy

surf the small web - a gemini, spartan and nex browser

## get cozy

```
$ go install blekksprut.net/cozy/cmd/cozy@latest
$ cozy
$ cozy nex://manatsu.town/ # head directly to an url
$ cozy -t day # always use the day theme
```

